markdownRemark.html: On Guarino's influence on the Latin grammar of Aldo Manuzio, see Robert Black, "Aldo Manuzio Grammarian," in Collectanea manuziana, ed. by P.D. Accendere and S. U. Baldassarri (Florence: Le Lettere, 2017), pp. 65-92, esp. 84-85.
